<L>__{interior danny's motel room later}
<A>__{alone he sits at the desk, finds himself gazing at the torah, standing in a corner of his closet, draped in the tallis. he slams the closet door, it bounces open. slams it again, making sure it latches. he sits down, looks at the closed door until, in bitter resignation he gets up and opens it again. he unrolls the torah on the bed...scotch tapes the tear closed...attempts to clean the stain with a moistened cloth.}
